<figure class="system-stack">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 760 430" role="img" aria-labelledby="stack-title stack-desc">
    <title id="stack-title">AI工程系统分层图</title>
    <desc id="stack-desc">从用户任务到Agent策略、模型与检索、工具协议、状态运行时和基础设施；评测与安全贯穿每一层。</desc>
    <defs>
      <marker id="stack-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0 0L10 5L0 10z" /></marker>
    </defs>
    <rect x="1" y="1" width="758" height="428" rx="18" class="system-stack__canvas" />
    <text x="42" y="46" class="system-stack__kicker">SYSTEM VIEW · 从需求走到可验证运行</text>

    <g class="system-stack__layers">
      <g transform="translate(42 70)"><rect width="550" height="48" rx="10" /><text x="18" y="29">01</text><text x="62" y="29">用户任务与交互</text><text x="530" y="29" text-anchor="end">输入 / 反馈</text></g>
      <g transform="translate(54 126)"><rect width="538" height="48" rx="10" /><text x="18" y="29">02</text><text x="62" y="29">Agent策略与工作流</text><text x="518" y="29" text-anchor="end">决策 / 边界</text></g>
      <g transform="translate(66 182)"><rect width="526" height="48" rx="10" /><text x="18" y="29">03</text><text x="62" y="29">模型、上下文与检索</text><text x="506" y="29" text-anchor="end">Token / 证据</text></g>
      <g transform="translate(78 238)"><rect width="514" height="48" rx="10" /><text x="18" y="29">04</text><text x="62" y="29">工具与协议</text><text x="494" y="29" text-anchor="end">Schema / 权限</text></g>
      <g transform="translate(90 294)"><rect width="502" height="48" rx="10" /><text x="18" y="29">05</text><text x="62" y="29">状态、运行时与队列</text><text x="482" y="29" text-anchor="end">取消 / 重试</text></g>
      <g transform="translate(102 350)"><rect width="490" height="48" rx="10" /><text x="18" y="29">06</text><text x="62" y="29">存储、网络与基础设施</text><text x="470" y="29" text-anchor="end">持久化 / 部署</text></g>
    </g>

    <g class="system-stack__rail">
      <rect x="620" y="70" width="98" height="328" rx="14" />
      <path d="M669 104 V359" marker-end="url(#stack-arrow)" />
      <text x="669" y="97" text-anchor="middle">EVIDENCE</text>
      <text x="669" y="213" text-anchor="middle" transform="rotate(-90 669 213)">评测 · 安全 · TRACE</text>
      <text x="669" y="385" text-anchor="middle">REPLAY</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption>课程不是从“调一个模型接口”开始，而是从输入、状态、边界和证据开始。</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .system-stack { margin: 1.2rem 0 2rem; }
  .system-stack svg { display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .system-stack__canvas { fill: var(--sl-color-gray-7); stroke: var(--sl-color-gray-5); }
  .system-stack__kicker { fill: var(--sl-color-gray-2); font-family: var(--sl-font-mono); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .05em; }
  .system-stack__layers rect { fill: var(--sl-color-bg); stroke: var(--sl-color-gray-5); stroke-width: 1.5; }
  .system-stack__layers g:nth-child(2) rect,
  .system-stack__layers g:nth-child(4) rect,
  .system-stack__layers g:nth-child(6) rect { fill: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sl-color-accent) 5%, var(--sl-color-bg)); }
  .system-stack__layers text { fill: var(--sl-color-text); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 650; }
  .system-stack__layers text:first-of-type { fill: var(--sl-color-accent-high); font-family: var(--sl-font-mono); font-size: 12px; }
  .system-stack__layers text:last-of-type { fill: var(--sl-color-gray-2); font-family: var(--sl-font-mono); font-size: 11px; }
  .system-stack__rail rect { fill: color-mix(in srgb, #16845c 9%, var(--sl-color-bg)); stroke: #16845c; stroke-width: 1.5; stroke-dasharray: 6 5; }
  .system-stack__rail path { fill: none; stroke: #16845c; stroke-width: 2; }
  .system-stack__rail marker path { fill: #16845c; }
  .system-stack__rail text { fill: color-mix(in srgb, #16845c 78%, var(--sl-color-text)); font-family: var(--sl-font-mono); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 750; letter-spacing: .05em; }
  .system-stack figcaption { margin-top: .6rem; color: var(--sl-color-gray-2); font-size: .78rem; text-align: center; }
</style>
